WINDOWS 7 SET UP
=*= Create your workspace first on wherever folder you want
=*= After installing xampp
    =*= open Xampp control panel
    =*= click on config button
    =*= click on Apache(httpd.conf)
    =*= find 
        DocumentRoot "C:/xampp/htdocs/"
        Directory "C:/xampp/htdocs/"
    =*= replace the folder to your workspace, so it change like this
        DocumentRoot "D:/Your/Workspace/Folder"
        Directory "D:/Your/Workspace/Folder"
    =*= save it and start on Apache Module
